  <body>
    <segment id="1" parent="5" relname="span">Biden’s reference to the press room as a swimming pool was a historical joke </segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="1" relname="antithesis">
rather than a sign of mental incapacity. </segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="6" relname="span">
This lie deserves the same scrutiny as the other whoppers from today, though, </segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="9" relname="same-unit">
because </segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="8" relname="attribution">
as Glenn Kessler accurately observed, </segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="10" relname="span">
Trump’s common pattern is projection.</segment>
<group id="6" type="span" />
<group id="5" type="span" parent="3" relname="concession" />
